        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0421P1_20040525_WH_72' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        3.9 pm
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0421P1_20040525_WH_73'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/miss-diane-abbott' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0421P1_20040525_WH_73' title='Link to this speech by Miss Diane Abbott' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/miss-diane-abbott" title="Miss Diane Abbott">Ms Diane Abbott</a></cite>
